": [111.8, 437.6, 408.1, 460.6]}, {"text": "1,096 $", "bbox": [606.0, 437.6, 675.6, 460.6]}, {"text": "998.88", "bbox": [729.3, 437.6, 803.3, 460.6]}, {"text": "7.4", "bbox": [886.4, 437.6, 917.6, 460.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [987.1, 437.6, 1007.8, 460.6]}, {"text": "705,684", "bbox": [1051.7, 437.6, 1126.1, 460.6]}, {"text": "Exercisable at December 31, 2015", "bbox": [111.8, 467.7, 403.4, 490.6]}, {"text": "272 $", "bbox": [621.8, 467.7, 675.6, 490.6]}, {"text": "721.35", "bbox": [729.3, 467.7, 803.3, 490.6]}, {"text": "4.8", "bbox": [886.4, 467.7, 917.6, 490.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [987.1, 467.7, 1007.8, 490.6]}, {"text": "250,617", "bbox": [1051.7, 467.7, 1126.1, 490.6]}, {"text": "RSUs", "bbox": [111.8, 523.9, 166.8, 546.9]}, {"text": "Outstanding at December 31, 2014", "bbox": [111.8, 548.9, 408.1, 571.9]}, {"text": "55", "bbox": [632.3, 548.9, 687.7, 571.9]}, {"text": "Granted", "bbox": [111.8, 574.7, 184.0, 597.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [632.3, 574.7, 687.7, 597.7]}, {"text": "Vested", "bbox": [111.8, 600.2, 174.8, 623.2]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [635.8, 600.2, 687.7, 623.2]}, {"text": "Forfeited", "bbox": [111.8, 625.7, 193.3, 648.7]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [635.8, 625.7, 687.7, 648.7]}, {"text": "Outstanding at December 31, 2015", "bbox": [111.8, 651.7, 408.1, 674.7]}, {"text": "51", "bbox": [632.3, 651.7, 687.7, 674.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [987.1, 651.7, 1007.8, 674.7]}, {"text": "83,340", "bbox": [1062.2, 651.7, 1126.1, 674.7]}, {"text": "Vested, but not issued at December 31, 2015", "bbox": [111.8, 682.0, 490.3, 705.0]}, {"text": "33", "bbox": [632.3, 682.0, 687.7, 705.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [987.1, 682.0, 1007.8, 705.0]}, {"text": "53,710", "bbox": [1062.2, 682.0, 1121.5, 705.0]}, {"text": "To estimate the grant-date fair value of its Options, the Company uses the Black-Scholes option-pricing model (the “Pricing", "bbox": [107.3, 734.5, 1147.2, 757.5]}, {"text": "Model”). The Pricing Model estimates the per share fair value of an option on its date of grant based on the following factors: the", "bbox": [56.3, 758.5, 1140.2, 781.5]}, {"text": "option’s exercise price; the price of the underlying stock on the date of grant; the estimated dividend yield; a risk-free interest rate; the", "bbox": [56.3, 782.5, 1180.9, 805.5]}, {"text": "estimated option term; and the expected volatility. For the risk-free interest rate, the Company uses U.S. Treasury STRIPS which", "bbox": [56.3, 806.5, 1138.1, 829.5]}, {"text": "mature at approximately the same time as the option’s expected holding term. For expected volatility, NVR has concluded that its", "bbox": [56.3, 830.3, 1143.1, 853.2]}, {"text": "historical volatility over the option’s expected holding term provides the most reasonable basis for this estimate. The fair value of the", "bbox": [56.3, 854.3, 1171.9, 877.3]}, {"text": "Options granted during 2015, 2014 and 2013 was estimated on the grant date using the Pricing Model, based on the following", "bbox": [56.3, 878.3, 1110.0, 901.3]}, {"text": "assumptions:", "bbox": [56.3, 898.5, 176.6, 926.2]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [679.0, 961.4, 716.5, 979.9]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [851.1, 961.4, 888.5, 979.9]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1023.7, 961.4, 1061.1, 979.9]}, {"text": "Estimated option life", "bbox": [111.8, 982.6, 291.8, 1005.5]}, {"text": "5.17 years", "bbox": [652.8, 982.6, 743.8, 1005.5]}, {"text": "5.16 years", "bbox": [824.8, 982.6, 915.9, 1005.5]}, {"text": "5.20 years", "bbox": [997.4, 982.6, 1088.5, 1005.5]}, {"text": "Risk free interest rate (range)", "bbox": [111.8, 1008.1, 361.2, 1031.1]}, {"text": "1.04%-2.07%", "bbox": [638.5, 1008.1, 786.8, 1031.1]}, {"text": "1.06%-2.49%", "bbox": [810.6, 1008.1, 964.3, 1031.1]}, {"text": "0.42%-2.10%", "bbox": [982.9, 1008.1, 1121.9, 1031.1]}, {"text": "Expected volatility (range)", "bbox": [111.8, 1033.6, 340.4, 1056.6]}, {"text": "17.00%-26.79%   18.26%-30.57%     17.98%-32.72%", "bbox": [609.7, 1033.6, 1121.9, 1056.6]}, {"text": "Expected dividend rate", "bbox": [111.8, 1059.1, 309.1, 1082.1]}, {"text": "0.00%", "bbox": [674.8, 1059.1, 733.7, 1082.1]}, {"text": "0.00%", "bbox": [846.8, 1059.1, 905.8, 1082.1]}, {"text": "0.00%", "bbox": [1019.2, 1059.1, 1078.1, 1082.1]}, {"text": "Weighted average grant-date fair value per share of", "bbox": [111.8, 1084.6, 545.7, 1107.6]}, {"text": "options granted", "bbox": [111.8, 1108.6, 261.9, 1131.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [614.5, 1108.6, 631.4, 1131.6]}, {"text": "296.50", "bbox": [673.0, 1108.6, 735.5, 1131.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [772.3, 1108.6, 803.4, 1131.6]}, {"text": "267.66", "bbox": [845.1, 1108.6, 907.6, 1131.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [944.1, 1108.6, 981.1, 1131.6]}, {"text": "268.13", "bbox": [1017.4, 1108.6, 1079.9, 1131.6]}, {"text": "In accordance with ASC 718, Compensation – Stock Compensation, the fair value of the RSUs is measured as if they were", "bbox": [107.3, 1161.4, 1134.7, 1184.3]}, {"text": "vested and issued on the grant date. Additionally, under ASC 718, service-only restrictions on vesting of RSUs are not reflected in the", "bbox": [56.3, 1185.4, 1179.5, 1208.4]}, {"text": "fair value calculation at the grant date. As a result, the fair value of the RSUs was the closing price of the Company’s common stock", "bbox": [56.3, 1209.4, 1165.4, 1232.4]}, {"text": "on the day immediately preceding the date of grant. There were no RSUs granted during 2015.", "bbox": [56.3, 1233.1, 855.6, 1256.1]}, {"text": "Compensation cost for Options and RSUs is recognized on a straight-line basis over the requisite service period for the entire", "bbox": [107.3, 1282.2, 1156.0, 1305.1]}, {"text": "award (from the date of grant through the period of the last separately vesting portion of the grant). For the recognition of equity-based", "bbox": [56.3, 1306.2, 1185.9, 1329.1]}, {"text": "compensation, the RSUs are treated as a separate award from the Options. Additionally, the Options which are subject to a", "bbox": [56.3, 1330.2, 1084.0, 1353.1]}, {"text": "performance condition are treated as a separate award from the “service-only” Options, and compensation expense is recognized when", "bbox": [56.3, 1354.2, 1184.2, 1377.2]}, {"text": "it becomes probable that the stated performance target will be achieved. The Company currently believes that it is probable that the", "bbox": [56.3, 1378.2, 1155.4, 1401.2]}, {"text": "performance condition will be satisfied at the target level and is recognizing compensation expense related to such Options", "bbox": [56.3, 1401.9, 1086.8, 1424.9]}, {"text": "accordingly. Compensation cost is recognized within the income statement in the same expense line as the cash compensation paid to", "bbox": [56.3, 1425.9, 1174.2, 1448.9]}, {"text": "the respective employees.", "bbox": [56.3, 1450.0, 281.3, 1472.9]}]}